story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_0300_10:
You outsider! Getting in my way again,
are you?!
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_1100_10:
Almighty Arceus above! Behold the
glorious conclusion to my effort!
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_1500_10: Cyrus! Why are you helping THEM?
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_1600_10:
Our goals are aligned! We BOTH want
to recreate this world!
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_1700_10:
I don’t see how you could control Arceus
if you can’t even awaken your arc suit.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_1900_10:
At this rate, it’s more likely Arceus would
accept someone from this side—and
grant them its power.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_2000_10: This decision is the obvious one.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_2200_10:
I don’t recall entering a pact with you in
the first place.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_2300_10:
Perhaps if you were a competent
merchant, you’d have written up
a contract.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_2500_10: Nothing good will come of this.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_2600_10: You all choose to mock me, then?
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_2800_10:
I’ll admit, I was unprepared this time.
But mark my words...I will be back.
story_arceus_06_10000/2401_1001_3000_10: I hope you don’t regret this later.
